Class ResponseLogin

java.lang.Object
in.devstream.openapi.model.ResponseLogin

Serializable
@Generated(value="org.openapitools.codegen.languages.SpringCodegen", comments="Generator version: 7.10.0") public class ResponseLogin extends Object implements Serializable
Check if requiresTwoFactorAuth is true, then use ID and generated OTP to send another request to get authentication tokens. If two factor authentication is set to false, directly access the tokens from the object.
